<h1>Schedule of Rent Arrears</h1>
<p><em>Wales - Renting Homes (Wales) Act 2016</em></p>
<p>Claim reference: {{claimant_reference}}</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Period</th>
      <th>Due date</th>
      <th>Amount due</th>
      <th>Amount paid</th>
      <th>Arrears</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {{#each arrears_schedule}}
    <tr>
      <td>{{period}}</td>
      <td>{{due_date}}</td>
      <td>{{currency amount_due}}</td>
      <td>{{currency amount_paid}}</td>
      <td>{{currency arrears}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
</table>

<p><strong>Total arrears:</strong> {{currency arrears_total}}</p>

<p>
  Attach proof of payments received, bank statements and rent ledgers behind this schedule. The County Court
  expects a clear period-by-period breakdown matching the occupation contract rent frequency.
</p>
